title: Alia Bhatt re-creates iconic saree look of Rekha from Silsila, pays tribute to her at Umrao Jaan screening
author: Santanu Das
description: Alia Bhatt took serious fashion inspiration from Rekha's look in Yash Chopra's Silsila as she graced the screening of Umrao Jaan.
